address.streetAddress: The Estrella Plan, The Vintage at River Oaks

location.fullValue: The Estrella Plan, The Vintage at River Oaks

data.description: Opportunity awaits to own a home on this approximately two acre usable lot located in a rural setting about six miles east of town. Enter under the front covered porch into living room, family room, dining area, open kitchen and half bath on the main living level. The functional kitchen offers stainless-steel appliances, solid surface countertops, a breakfast bar, plenty of storage and a large pantry. Upstairs you will find a master suite with full bath and walk-in closet, two additional bedrooms and additional full bath. There is plenty of room on this property for trailer and/or RV. Complete with an attached two car garage with laundry hook-ups. Come enjoy the country lifestyle while close to town, shopping and dining with many beautiful wineries and vineyards nearby.
